data.title: Dallas Stars Colors
data.meta_description: The Dallas Stars colors are victory green, silver, black and white. Here are the Dallas Stars team color codes if you need them for any of your digital projects. Follow this link for the rest of the NHL hex color codes for all of your favorite NHL team color codes.
data.text:
The Dallas Stars colors are Victory green, silver, black, and white. The Dallas Stars team colors in Hex, RGB, and CMYK can be found below. The Dallas Stars are a team from Dallas, Texas. The biggest rivals of the Dallas Stars are the St. Louis Blues.

Dallas Stars Primary Logo Colors

The primary colors of the Dallas Stars can be found in the table below.

Dallas Stars Pantone Color Codes

The Dallas Stars NHL team Pantone colors are 3425 C for Victory green, 429 C for silver, and BLACK C for black.

The Victory green Pantone color of the Dallas Stars can be found below.

PMS 3425 C

The silver Pantone color of the Dallas Stars can be found below.

PMS 429 C

The black Pantone color of the Dallas Stars can be found below.

PMS PROCESS BLACK C

Dallas Stars Color Codes HEX

The Dallas Stars colors HEX codes are #006847 for Victory green, #8F8F8C for silver, and #111111 for black.

The Victory green HEX color code for the Dallas Stars ice hockey team can be found below.

#006847

The silver HEX colour code for the Dallas Stars can be found below.

#8F8F8C

The black HEX colour code for the Dallas Stars can be found below.

#111111

Dallas Stars Color Codes RGB

The Dallas Stars colors RGB codes are (0,104,71) for Victory green, (143,143,140) for silver, and (17,17,17) for black colour.

The Victory green RGB color code for the Dallas Stars can be found below.

(0, 104, 71)

The silver RGB colour code for the Dallas Stars can be found below.

(143, 143, 140)

The black RGB colour code for the Dallas Stars can be found below.

(17, 17, 17)

Dallas Stars Color Codes CMYK

The Dallas Stars colors CMYK codes are (93,13,85,44) for Victory green, (21,11,9,23) for silver, and (0,0,0,100) for black color.

The Victory green CMYK color code for the Dallas Stars can be found below.

(93, 13, 85, 44)

The silver CMYK colour code for the Dallas Stars can be found below.

(21, 11, 9, 23)

The black CMYK colour code for the Dallas Stars can be found below.

(0, 0, 0, 100)

Dallas Stars Logo Colors

The Dallas Stars logo colors are Victory green, silver, and black. The Victory green color code for the Dallas Stars logo is PANTONE: PMS 3425 C, HEX COLOR: #006847, RGB: (0, 104, 71), CMYK: (93, 13, 85, 44). The silver color code for the Dallas Stars logo is PANTONE: PMS 429 C, HEX COLOR: #8F8F8C, RGB: (143,143,140), CMYK: (21, 11, 9, 23). The black color code for the Dallas Stars logo is PANTONE: PMS PROCESS BLACK C, HEX COLOR: #111111, RGB: (17, 17, 17), CMYK: (0, 0, 0, 100).

Dallas Stars Logo

The Dallas Stars logo has Victory green, silver, and black colors and a monogram consisting of a letter D and a star behind it. The Dallas Stars logo meaning symbolizes the combination of the city’s initial and its name.

Dallas Stars Logo Fonts

The Dallas Stars logo font is NHL Dallas. The NHL Dallas font is used for jersey lettering, player names, numbers, team logo, branding, and merchandise.

Dallas Stars Jersey

The Dallas Stars jersey colors are Victory green, silver, black, and white. The Dallas Stars uniform has been the same since 2013. The Dallas Stars jersey in an image format can be found below.
